The paper also discusses the use of prioritized replay, which suggests that it may belong to the cs.SY (Systems and Control) sub-category. The paper also discusses the empirical performance of the proposed algorithm, which suggests that it may belong to the cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-category.
